               <scopecontent id="aspace_eddbf65ec2602df22f4729daa84718e0">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>The photograph album contains circa 197 photographs, primarily family photographs of the Solberg family in Montana.  Present are family portraits, candids, and photographs of holiday celebrations and vacations, including a trip to Yellowstone National Park.</p>
