               </did>
               <scopecontent id="aspace_705136cb2f3a6a1e94ee76e04845a774">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Photograph album containing circa 513 photographs.  Early photographs document Helen Solberg Fowler's time as a student at Montana State University, including photographs of campus and her recreational activities. Also present are photographs from her career as a teacher in Darby, Montana and her family life in Big Timber and Darby, Montana.</p>
               </scopecontent>
