               <scopecontent id="aspace_86be0f2122642750ff75d129f23717e3">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Scrapbook containing clippings, ephemera, and correspondence compiled by Helen Solberg Fowler. Present are invitations, programs, and clippings related to social and cultural events in Montana, including sorority events  at Montana State University and activities for Solberg's church and the Young Women's Christian Association (YWCA).</p>
